                registers
            </li>
            <li>
                Modbus Data Writing: Configure function code (e.g., write single
                register 06H) to achieve control of devices such as frequency
                converters
            </li>
            <li>
                Bus Sensor Application: Wiring and data reading of DS18B20
                single-bus temperature sensors (if 485 function is not selected)
            </li>
            <li>
                Bus Data as a Condition: Utilizing temperature, humidity, and
                ammeter data read by Modbus as conditions for automation control
            </li>
